      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="en-US">
        <seg>Comcast understands&lt;/g1&gt; the power of global open source collaboration and innovation and &lt;g2&gt;it is a vital tool for working on its customer experience and to attract&lt;/g2&gt; the best talent to the company.</seg>
