      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="en-US">
        <seg>Comcast ’s involvement in open source officially began in 2006, when a software developer made a patch contribution to Apache HTTP and demonstrated that fixing a project upstream was easier than maintaining patches at the consumption level.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="ja-JP" changeid="tani" changedate="20220515T030809Z" creationid="tani" creationdate="20220312T080645Z">
