    <tu>
      <tuv lang="en-US">
        <seg>Spurred by the rapid growth of Tesla and its software-first automotive technology development approach, Volkwagen has created a number of initiatives to accelerate the internal creation of software, as well as participation in open source communities and projects.</seg>
